--- Lokk / Axis ---

Axis replies to Windlord, "All right, Lokk, Seekker and I are on it." He is about to turn around, when Seekker hits him from behind, "Whoa there Seekker, attack who? Them? Naw! They are going to be joining us." Axis shrugs apologetically to Hazel and her team.
  Lokk also frowns, "Seekker, calm down... err TRY to calm down..." Lokk smiles at the new bots, "Anyway, this is Seekker, the third half of our team. No wait, that would be the third third..." Lokk starts thinking to himself, unintentionally ignoring everyone else. 
  Axis taps Seekker on the shoulder and introduces the bots, "This is Hazel, Cerulean, Bronze, Periwinkle, Pink, White and Brown, a new addition to our faction, the Chivitrons. Hazel and crew, meet Seekker, who's name you've already heard." He nods as a sign of courteous respect.
